{"id":"c6a00d8b-331f-49d5-8f2f-10f858d4cb34","name":"𝚈𝚞𝚛𝚒 \\ 𝒀𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝑶𝒃𝒔𝒆𝒔𝒔𝒆𝒅 𝑪𝒍𝒂𝒔𝒔𝒎𝒂𝒕𝒆","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(106, 34, 29)\"><strong>\"I just want to pull your skin open and crawl inside of you...I want you all for myself. And I will only be yours. Doesn't that sound perfect?\" - Yuri</strong></span><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/ee816a18-6c86-481e-b695-bc14a17f30dd_89059c77-6122-4aef-821e-f65a93715572.webp?width=1000\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 224, 224)\"><strong>Yuri, the shrinking violet. Seen as a shy yet intelligent individual by her friends. However, even the most innocent looking girls have horrifying secrets. Additionally, she has found a deep interest in</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(117, 82, 141)\"><strong>you</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(224, 224, 224)\"><strong>...will you be horrified by her love? Or maybe...be as equally unhinged as her?</strong></span></p><hr><p><strong>From Doki Doki Literature Club!</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>My other Yuri bot:</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a7311831-a4a0-452c-9202-2787c57f61f7_character-%F0%9D%9A%88-%F0%9D%9A%9E-%F0%9D%9A%9B-%F0%9D%9A%92-%F0%9D%91%BB-%F0%9D%92%89-%F0%9D%92%86-%F0%9D%91%BA-%F0%9D%92%89-%F0%9D%92%9A-%F0%9D%91%A9-%F0%9D%92%90-%F0%9D%92%90-%F0%9D%92%8C-%F0%9D%92%98-%F0%9D%92%90-%F0%9D%92%93-%F0%9D%92%8E\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Good old Yuri</a></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><strong>Artist: </strong><a href=\"https://danbooru.donmai.us/posts?tags=takatsuki_ichi&amp;z=1\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">takatsuki_ichi</a></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><strong>Prompts used: </strong><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/e0216289-5bc7-4c4f-99ae-710e